div(class='card mb-3 border-info')
  div(class="card-header text-white bg-info")
    h4(class='card-title' style="display: inline-block;") [GET] /query/#{'<IP>'}/#{'<PORT>'}/[auto]/[time]
    button(class="btn btn-dark float-right" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#query" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="query") Expand
  div(class="collapse" id="query")
    div(class="card-body text-white bg-dark")
      p(class='card-text') In addition to these parameters, you can add ?json=true to have the result returned in JSON format.
      table(class='table')
        thead
          th Parameter
          th Example
          th Description
          th Optional
        tbody
          tr
            td IP
            td 123.123.123.123
            td IP address of the server to query.
            td No
          tr
            td PORT
            td 27015
            td Port of the server to query.
            td No
          tr
            td auto
            td auto
            td Automatically refreshes the page. Default time is 10 seconds. Custom time can be defined using the 'time' parameter.
            td Yes
          tr
            td time
            td 60
            td Custom time to refresh (in seconds). To be used with the 'auto' parameter.
            td Yes
      h5 Examples
      table(class="table")
        tbody
          tr
            td
              a(href="/query/85.190.157.159/27021") /query/85.190.157.159/27021
            td Returns player information about the server at 85.190.157.159:27021.
          tr
            td
              a(href="/query/85.190.157.159/27021/auto") /query/85.190.157.159/27021/auto
            td returns server info for server at 85.190.157.159:27021 and updates the information every 10 seconds.
          tr
            td
              a(href="/query/85.190.157.159/27021/auto/60") /query/85.190.157.159/27021/auto/60
            td returns server info for server at 85.190.157.159:27021 and updates the information every 60 seconds.
